"><span class=\"red\">保留以往真香港嘅紀錄<br />\n香港以前唔係咁<br />\n唔好比小朋友以為香港一直都係冇自由</span></span>"},{"pid":"816a573b25e1bc54e4c6a8f950df919905b5b5e3","tid":2511901,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:13:56.000Z","msg":"一早知你想咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57c504552960315fd9acdea8e5df1a7513abb6a","tid":2511901,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"push啊<br />\n上熱門啊"},{"pid":"adcf6323c14d7850b518ae1a4812afde01f6fd2e","tid":2511901,"uid":242921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"屌，快d download晒d古今風雲人物先"},{"pid":"147065273c1e0d39a19fddce1d0e58cef1a307ee","tid":2511901,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:19:07.000Z","msg":"backup師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d4087a9a30f1c24d308e0859320c00321fdec8","tid":2511901,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6cd715b2cc0a812ad65a9a733c90afddfa9621","tid":2511901,"uid":383943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b0f5ffc478b0ea652b8305457c73191a6ee59f2","tid":2511901,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:14:32.000Z","msg":"【 李百全或再出手整頓網絡重溫港台舊節目期限 】<br />\n<br />\n廣播道總台於短短兩個月內徹底變天，令很多港台中人都意興闌珊，不過「變革」未完，踏入五月，外界稱為「生抽王」的李百全將會再出手整頓，而今次針對的，是YouTube上架的舊節目。一直以來，港台製作的影像及聲音內容，<a href=\"http://於播出後的一年之內都可以在香港電台網站www.rthk.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%96%BC%E6%92%AD%E5%87%BA%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%8B%E5%85%A7%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.rthk.hk&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=c3022c1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">於播出後的一年之內都可以在香港電台網站www.rthk.hk</a>重溫，不過本站今日（1/5）收到可靠消息指，李百全已通知相關同事，「節目於播出之後一年下架」的標準，將會有只限港台網站，延伸至YouTube。<br />\n<br />\n雖然暫時未有確實執行日期，但假如成事，所有在YouTube港台頻道上架超過一年的舊內容，包括《頭條新聞》、《視點31》、《議事論事》，以及《鏗鏘集》的「7.21元朗黑夜」（2019年7月29日上架／<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3xx1c2O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3xx1c2O&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=b4d5302a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3xx1c2O</a>） 均會在新措施生效後悉數下架，而《鏗鏘集》的「7.21誰主真相」（<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3td3Wz0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3td3Wz0&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=a8c5112e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3td3Wz0</a>） ，於2020年7月13日上架，故估計亦會在今年7月13日之後刪除，而一直在社交網絡廣傳、2016年2月1日上架的《文化樹下：黃霑・好中國》（<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3nJXz59\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3nJXz59&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=9b060961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3nJXz59</a>） ，亦難逃遭下架的命運，這條短片至今已累積接近300萬點擊，而《鏗鏘集》兩集關於「7.21元朗襲擊事件」的YouTube瀏覽次數，截至今天下午5時，分別有130萬及155萬。<br />\n<br />\n（01052021）<br />\n<br />\n#游大東 #游大東影視筆記 #香港電台 香港電台視像新聞 RTHK VNEWS RTHK 香港電台 港台電視部－公共事務組 香港電台視點31 鏗鏘集 Hong Kong Connection 潘小濤 葉一知 羅冠聰 Nathan Law William on the way 快樂的 眾新聞 做乜膠睇電視 我睇咗啲乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100044233459246/posts/331107498373696/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100044233459246%2Fposts%2F331107498373696%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=c40fedc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100044233459246/posts/331107498373696/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:25:03.000Z","msg":"歷史由我創<br />\n來緊睇下李八存可以坐邊個焗腸位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 